LIFEOGRAPH FOR WINDOWS RELEASE HISTORY
======================================

0.4.1 - 2016-11-01

    * Bug fixes



0.4.0 - 2016-09-03

    * Added preliminary support for parametric tags
    * Implemented renaming tags
    * Implemented dismissing tags
    * Added a basic read-only mode



0.3.0 - 2016-01-17

    * Added support for diary format 1030
    * Added support for todo lists in entries
    * Added support for numeric and bullet lists in entries



0.2.0 - 2015-02-16

    * Converted the entry list into a tree view
    * Added support for chapters
    * Implemented searching text within entries
    * Added filtering by status, being favorite, and tag
    * Implemented editing entry date/number
    * Implemented marking entries as favorite
    * Implemented setting entry completion status
    * Added a tag list to the tag dialog



0.1.1 - 2014-12-16

    * Fixed crash when dismissing entries
    * Added 32x32 and 64x64 versions of the main icon



0.1.0 - 2014-12-13

    * Initial release

